1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,220
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:15,199 --> 00:00:17,879
(Wuhuduandao Sect)
Dasheng, you have one month

4
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:19,280
to go to Gusu
and break off the engagement.

5
00:00:19,280 --> 00:00:21,280
You must return to the sect by then.

6
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:23,079
(Peng Dasheng, Wuhuduandao Sect)
No delays.

7
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:23,759
(Peng Dasheng, Wuhuduandao Sect)

8
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,120
(Peng Dasheng, Wuhuduandao Sect)
Master...

9
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,559
I finally got to leave the mountain.

10
00:00:27,879 --> 00:00:29,320
Can't you let me
enjoy a few more days out here?

11
00:00:30,879 --> 00:00:31,920
You little rascal.

12
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:32,960
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

13
00:00:33,479 --> 00:00:35,320
(Master Xuanzhen, Wuhuduandao Sect)
You were born with sealed meridians.

14
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,280
Your destined tribulation
comes at twenty.

15
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:39,960
Your twentieth birthday
is only a month away.

16
00:00:40,719 --> 00:00:42,840
Death is already waiting for you.

17
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:43,280
You...

18
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:44,880
You're still thinking about having fun?

19
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:46,159
Master,

20
00:00:46,159 --> 00:00:47,920
ever since I was six,

21
00:00:48,039 --> 00:00:49,759
you've always said
I was destined to die young.

22
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,679
But look at me.
I'm still alive and kicking, aren't I?

23
00:00:51,799 --> 00:00:52,960
You should worry about yourself.

24
00:00:53,799 --> 00:00:55,640
Keep eating those roast chickens,

25
00:00:55,719 --> 00:00:57,320
and you might leave this world
before I do.

26
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:05,480
These pills will last you a month.

27
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:09,599
Remember, take one every day.

28
00:01:09,879 --> 00:01:11,560
Miss even one dose,

29
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,120
and your meridians will be shattered.

30
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,400
Got it.

31
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:16,760
And one more thing.

32
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:19,680
The soul jade your father left you...

33
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,480
Remember, you must...

34
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,319
You absolutely must...

35
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:26,560
Oh, Master.

36
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,799
Enough with the lectures.

37
00:01:27,799 --> 00:01:28,879
Just leave already.

38
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,599
Keep stalling,
and I'll be preparing your funeral.

39
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,159
Fine, fine.

40
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,079
I'm going. I'm going!

41
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:36,920
Master, why didn't you tell
Peng the truth?

42
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,040
Fate is shrouded in mist.

43
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,560
The more you seek answers,
the more confused you become.

44
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:45,560
Some tribulations
must be experienced firsthand

45
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:47,040
before one can truly understand them.

46
00:01:48,180 --> 00:01:48,620
Hyah!

47
00:02:01,140 --> 00:02:01,900
Hyah!

48
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,439
Such a handsome young man...

49
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:55,199
Why are you soaking alone
in this icy pool?

50
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:14,560
Come, join me for a bath.

51
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,159
A beauty inviting me?

52
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,639
How could I say no?

53
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,159
But...

54
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:25,400
Your illusion technique
may be convincing,

55
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,599
yet it can't fool my eyes.

56
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:02,700
(Mu Xiao, Holy Envoy of the Wudu Sect)

57
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,759
Dear ladies,

58
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:07,000
I think you've mistaken me
for someone else.

59
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:08,120
Don't act like we're close!

60
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:11,759
Miss, he doesn't seem like someone
from the Demon Sect.

61
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,599
Young man, you're quite impressive.

62
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,599
To see through

63
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:17,319
our Wudu Sect's
snake gu technique at a glance...

64
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,920
May I ask your name?

65
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,399
Peng Dasheng,

66
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:22,439
from Wuhuduandao Sect.

67
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:24,160
Wuhuduandao Sect?

68
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,360
Never heard of it.

69
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:28,120
Sounds like some tiny sect
hidden away in the middle of nowhere.

70
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,639
Just a bunch of frogs in a well.

71
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,959
Xiao, let's go.

72
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,959
Wait.

73
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:36,759
Ladies,

74
00:04:37,439 --> 00:04:39,839
my horse broke its leg because of you.

75
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:42,199
How are you going to make this right?

76
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,920
Take the money and leave.

77
00:04:51,980 --> 00:04:54,260
(Duan Qingyao,
Holy Maiden of the Wudu Sect)

78
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:59,000
I don't want your money.

79
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:03,639
I want an apology to my horse.

80
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,519
Young man,

81
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:17,439
weren't you the one who wanted me

82
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:22,920
to apologize to your horse?

83
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:25,920
Miss, if you don't want
to apologize, fine.

84
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,079
There's no need
to start fighting, right?

85
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:28,800
You finally know you were wrong?

86
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:29,879
Too late!

87
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,839
Miss, I don't hit women.

88
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,319
But I hit men.

89
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,639
Why do you always attack below the belt?

90
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:12,920
Enough talk.
If you have the guts, take my move.

91
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,519
Miss,

92
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:43,839
can you just hear me out?

93
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,439
You shameless lecher! I'll kill you!

94
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:56,120
(He doesn't have
the slightest bit of inner force.)

95
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,040
You coward!

96
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,480
Don't let me see you again!

97
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,600
Good thing she's gone.

98
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:18,639
Seriously, how is that girl

99
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:20,279
even fiercer than a mountain tiger?

100
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,839
Dashuai, stop pretending.

101
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:29,439
They're gone. Get up.

102
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,040
Come on. I'll buy you some buns.

103
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,600
Let's go.

104
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,839
Enjoy. Come again next time.

105
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:52,120
Fresh buns, sir.

106
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:53,240
Hot out of the oven!

107
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,279
They're delicious!

108
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,639
I'll take them all.

109
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:56,879
All of them?

110
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:59,800
Then I can close early today.

111
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,040
Look at these giant buns.

112
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,240
(The money Master gave me is all gone?)

113
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,439
(I shouldn't have tried to show off.)

114
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,560
Boss.

115
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,600
One, please.

116
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:15,839
Just one?

117
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,439
One.

118
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,920
Don't have that much money, huh?

119
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,199
Then stop pretending you're rich.

120
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,240
What a cheapskate.

121
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,720
Yeah, yeah, I know.

122
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,759
Medicine first, then food.

123
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,879
What's happening here?

124
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,480
Hurry, move!

125
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,679
What's going on?

126
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:01,640
(Zhang's Bun Stand)

127
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,720
My pills...

128
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,399
How dare you!

129
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:11,320
Stop right there!

130
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,640
Hyah!

131
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:33,100
(Fang Xiaojiu,
daughter of the Sifang Escort Agency)

132
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,879
Father!

133
00:09:40,159 --> 00:09:43,159
Xiaojiu, run!

134
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:47,440
Father!

135
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,480
Miss, we have to leave!

136
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:49,799
Father!

137
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,240
Go!

138
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:59,080
(The Demon Sect
slaughtered my entire family.)

139
00:09:59,759 --> 00:10:01,480
(This is a blood feud.)

140
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,279
Miss, please eat something.

141
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,759
You sure run fast.

142
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:43,200
My shoes are about worn out chasing you.

143
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:47,759
A few broken blades?

144
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:48,919
Who are you trying to scare?

145
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,639
Oh, me?

146
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:53,679
Come on. Aim right here.

147
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:55,000
Slit my throat. Go ahead.

148
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,960
I'm telling you to do it, but you won't?

149
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,200
Didn't your parents teach you

150
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,279
to apologize after hurting someone?

151
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,200
You have no manners.

152
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,879
Luckily,

153
00:11:13,279 --> 00:11:14,279
I'm a forgiving man.

154
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:17,679
I'll let it go this time.

155
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:20,200
I have things to do.
I'll be leaving now.

156
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,759
Weren't you acting all brave just now?

157
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,399
Why are you backing off?

158
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,000
Sir.

159
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,720
It was just a misunderstanding.

160
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:32,519
A misunderstanding?

161
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:35,159
Go explain that to the King of Hell.

162
00:11:44,820 --> 00:11:45,540
♪Come on♪

163
00:11:48,820 --> 00:11:50,500
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

164
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:55,460
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

165
00:11:55,700 --> 00:11:58,700
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

166
00:11:58,860 --> 00:12:01,780
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

167
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:04,700
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

168
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,240
One.

169
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,519
Two.

170
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:08,679
Three.

171
00:12:08,679 --> 00:12:14,420
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

172
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,580
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

173
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:20,500
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

174
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:23,460
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

175
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,440
That's all? You're already down?

176
00:12:29,559 --> 00:12:30,679
A bunch of useless fools.

177
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:32,360
All of you, get out of my way.

178
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:38,840
Senior Brother,
you still won't show yourself?

179
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,120
Could it be you're afraid?

180
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:48,840
(Soul)

181
00:12:56,820 --> 00:12:57,300
♪Come on♪

182
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:02,500
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

183
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:07,420
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

184
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:10,620
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

185
00:13:10,860 --> 00:13:13,700
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

186
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:16,700
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

187
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:20,180
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

188
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:23,420
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

189
00:13:23,580 --> 00:13:26,500
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

190
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:29,420
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

191
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:33,300
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

192
00:13:33,340 --> 00:13:36,340
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

193
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:42,020
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

194
00:13:42,420 --> 00:13:44,460
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

195
00:13:45,020 --> 00:13:47,540
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

196
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:50,660
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

197
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:54,460
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

198
00:13:55,060 --> 00:13:57,180
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

199
00:13:58,100 --> 00:14:00,220
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

200
00:14:00,380 --> 00:14:03,660
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

201
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:07,980
♪I am my own king♪

202
00:14:21,060 --> 00:14:22,620
♪I emerge into the world♪

203
00:14:22,620 --> 00:14:24,380
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

204
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:25,740
♪My pride is my trump card♪

205
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,540
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

206
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:28,940
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

207
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,700
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

208
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:32,220
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

209
00:14:32,220 --> 00:14:33,940
♪I dare to break every rule♪

210
00:14:33,940 --> 00:14:35,260
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

211
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:37,100
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

212
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,340
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

213
00:14:38,340 --> 00:14:40,580
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

214
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:42,100
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

215
00:14:42,100 --> 00:14:43,700
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

216
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:45,300
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

217
00:14:45,300 --> 00:14:47,020
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

218
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:48,740
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

219
00:14:48,740 --> 00:14:50,100
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

220
00:14:50,100 --> 00:14:51,740
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

221
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:53,220
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

222
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:54,940
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

223
00:14:54,940 --> 00:14:56,540
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

224
00:14:56,540 --> 00:14:58,100
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

225
00:14:58,100 --> 00:15:02,420
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

226
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:04,580
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

227
00:15:04,580 --> 00:15:07,180
♪Let me write the legend♪

228
00:15:12,060 --> 00:15:14,620
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

229
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:17,940
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

230
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:20,420
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

231
00:15:20,420 --> 00:15:24,500
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

232
00:15:24,860 --> 00:15:27,460
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

233
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:29,940
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

234
00:15:29,940 --> 00:15:32,980
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

235
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:38,020
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
